graph TD
    Landing[Landing Page] --> Header
    Landing --> Hero[Hero Section]
    Landing --> Features[Features/Benefits]
    Landing --> CTA[Call to Action]
    Landing --> About[About Us]
    Landing --> FAQ[FAQ Section]
    Landing --> Footer

    %% Header Section
    Header --> Logo
    Header --> Nav[Navigation Menu]
    Header --> Search
    Header --> UserMenu[User Menu]

    %% Hero Section
    Hero --> HeroTitle[Main Title]
    Hero --> HeroDesc[Description]
    Hero --> HeroImage[Platform Image]

    %% Features Section
    Features --> Feature1[Platform Management]
    Features --> Feature2[User Analytics]
    Features --> Feature3[Business Tools]
    Features --> Feature4[Security Features]

    %% CTA Section
    CTA --> CreateAccount[Create Account]
    CTA --> Login[Log In]
    
    CreateAccount --> RegistrationForm[Registration Form]
    Login --> LoginForm[Login Form]

    %% About Us Section
    About --> Mission[Mission Statement]
    About --> Vision[Vision]
    About --> Team[Team Info]

    %% FAQ Section
    FAQ --> FAQSearch[FAQ Search]
    FAQ --> Categories[FAQ Categories]
    FAQ --> Popular[Popular Questions]

    %% Footer Section
    Footer --> Links[Quick Links]
    Footer --> Contact[Contact Info]
    Footer --> Social[Social Media]
    Footer --> Legal[Legal Info]

    %% Styling
    classDef sectionTitle fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    class Landing,Header,Hero,Features,CTA,About,FAQ,Footer sectionTitle
